## 错误处理规范

### Service 层
```dart
// 返回 Result<T> 或使用自定义异常
class AppException implements Exception {
  final String message;
  final String? code;
  AppException(this.message, {this.code});
}

// ✅
Future<Result<List<Transaction>>> getTransactions() async {
  try {
    final list = await _dao.getAll();
    return Result.success(list);
  } catch (e, stack) {
    _logger.e('获取账单失败', error: e, stackTrace: stack);
    return Result.failure(AppException('获取账单失败', code: 'DB_ERROR'));
  }
}
```

### UI 层
```dart
// 统一使用 SnackBar / Dialog 展示错误
// ✅
ref.read(transactionProvider.notifier).load().then((result) {
  result.when(
